### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### API Info
GET http://localhost:3001/api

### Create a Conversation
POST http://localhost:3001/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Conversation",
  "projectId": "project-123"
}

### Send a Chat Message
POST http://localhost:3001/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello, Claude! Can you help me write a simple Python function?",
  "conversationId": "conv-123",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful coding assistant."
    }
  ]
}

### Stream a Chat Response
POST http://localhost:3001/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Write a short story about a robot learning to paint.",
  "conversationId": "conv-123",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a creative writer."
    }
  ]
}

### Get Conversations
GET http://localhost:3001/api/conversations

### Test with Multiple Messages
POST http://localhost:3001/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Can you make it more efficient?",
  "conversationId": "conv-123",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful coding assistant."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Write a function to calculate factorial"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here's a simple factorial function in Python:\n\n```python\ndef factorial(n):\n    if n == 0 or n == 1:\n        return 1\n    else:\n        return n * factorial(n - 1)\n```"
    }
  ]
}